subSubSection.paragraph: Due to the large number of changes to taxonomy conducted in the present study, several of which had to be supported by the selection of lectotypes , as well as the numerous new taxa described a taxonomic summary is presented to provide better overview. The following are lists of the genera and species newly described, lectotypes designated and all taxonomic changes arranged in alphabetical order.

n. sp.
